3.3 DUIM-Extended-Geometry Module

rectangle?

Generic function

Summary

Returns #t if the object is a rectangle.

Signature

rectangle? object => boolean

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

boolean
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-extended-geometry

Module

duim-extended-geometry

Description

Returns #t if object is a rectangle, otherwise returns #f.
